關鍵字(中)
直接訴權抗辯無因性理論準資金關係資金關係支付系統


關鍵字(英)
direct claimpayment systemdefense of instrumentquasi-funding relationshipVoraussetzungslosigkeit theoryfunding relationship


學科別分類



中文摘要
票據資金關係與準資金關係如原因關係般於票據之無因性理論中亦佔有舉足輕重地位。資金關係、準資金關係與票據關係間之互動態樣豐富多元，反應在票據債務人可否援引資金關係之抗辯來拒絕票據債務之履行。故本文先由票據行為之性質出發來探討票據權利之發生時點，而於票據權利發生後，再深入研討票據關係與分票據關係間之可能牽連與分割。藉由票據抗辯的觀點切入來檢視票據無因性理論有無修正之必要與得失。     因為資金關係涉及支付系統，故本文亦梗要介紹了我國目前支付系統之現況，並依據票據種類來個別觀察資金關係與支付系統之關聯。希冀透過資金關係之定義、性質與內涵之掌握，來釐清資金關係所可能產生之各種複雜法律關係。     就資金關係對支付系統之可能影響，除提出票據法有明文規範之直接訴權、利益返還請求權外，本文更試圖以金融實務上多所習見之票據與交易實況，來深入研究資金關係與票據關係間之可能牽連，並對無因性理論提出修正建議。


英文摘要
The relationships of funding and quasi-funding are just as important as the causing relationship with the Voraussetzungslosigkeit theory of instrument. The multiple reactions among the funding, quasi-funding and instrument relationship also indicate that whether the instrument debtors could defense not activating instrument obligation by using funding relationship. This thesis will discuss the timeline of causing rights of instrument by leading the properties of instrument behavior. In additional, it will continue to investigate the possibility of conjunction and separation between the instrument and separated-instrument relationship.  Thus, it is necessary and possible to modify the Voraussetzungslosigkeit theory from the view of the defense of instrument.   Since the funding relationship having connection with payment system, the article introduces the current payment system of The Republic of China (Taiwan).  Furthermore, it discusses the relevance regarding to the funding relationship and payment system of various types of instruments. The aim of this thesis is to use the definition, property, and contents of funding relationship to clarify the various complex legal relationships.   For the probable influences of funding relationship to payment system, it provides the direct claims and claims for the return of interest in the law of instruments. Besides, it also discusses the connection between the funding and instrument relationship from the financial practice and indicates the comments of amending the Voraussetzungslosigkeit theory.


論文目次
